Package bus

Class SingletonHashMapCollection

java.lang.Object
bus.SingletonHashMapCollection
public class SingletonHashMapCollection extends Object
Represents the collection of Vehicle in the Vehicles' Fleet Factory. Stores a HashMap that associates the serialNumber of the Vehicle object with the Vehicle object itself and provides the public services to manage the collection.
Version:
2021-12-14
Author:
Lilas Guan
